          </li>
          <li>
            <figure class="img-box pangram-underline">
              <img src="assets/img/pangram-underline-light.png?{{version}}" alt="Pangrams are underlined" />
            </figure>
            <p>In the result list pangrams are marked with a yellow underline.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
